/* Issue */Jagat Gosain as per my existing knowledge was never given the honor of having a suffix of Begum. Her title is believed to be Taj bibi, not Begum. The Begum word was added post to those women's titles who had a name with Begum, like Mariam-uz-Zamani and Nur Jahan.
